Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.11,0:18:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Trẻ sơ sinh à?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.11,0:18:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Tên Ban chết tiệt. \NViết bậy viết bạ...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.91,0:18:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Cao 5,1 ft, nặng 108 lb. Cain!!
